high_descs: Turn right and take a step forward, then turn left and walk up to the counter.
Pick up the potato off of the counter.
Turn around and walk forward, then turn right and walk over to the door, turn right to face the microwave.

Open the microwave and put the potato inside then close the door and turn on the microwave, after a couple seconds open the microwave back up and take the now heated potato out, then close the microwave.
Look down at the kitchen sink.
Put the heated potato in the kitchen sink on the left side.
anns.task_desc: Put a heated potato in the sink.

high_descs: take two steps to the right
pick up the potato that is on the counter
turn left, walk across room, turn right to face microwave
put potato in microwave, turn it on, take potato out when it turns off
take a step to the right
put the potato in the sink
anns.task_desc: put cooked potato in the sink

high_descs: Pick up the potato on the counter.
Turn left and walk to the microwave.
Heat the potato in the microwave.
Place the potato in the sink, to the left of the apple.
anns.task_desc: Place a heated potato in a sink.
